title: Pompeii.3D.2014.1080p.FullScreen.DTS5.1.MP4Plex
description:
This is about as good as you're going to get with full screen high resolution, and DTS 5.1 audio.

As always, I ask that you limit the route between source and destination via connecting your 3D TV, switch/router, and Plex Media Server so that wireless is not a factor in choppy playback, and wired ethernet rules the world of high quality performance.

ALWAYS LIMIT THE DISTANCE BETWEEN SOURCE AND DESTINATION when you want the best results (at least in high tech data sources, anyway ;-).

And PLEASE SEED at least 3X the source file size when enjoying highly distributable value!!!

Thanx OM  :)
